      <title>盗窃数十亿美元加密货币的首领被判处 5 年有期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/leader-of-crypto-heist-worth-billions-gets-five-year-sentence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有史以来最大的比特币盗窃案之一的主谋因与其社交媒体说唱歌手妻子合谋入侵 Bitfinex 交易所并抢走目前价值数十亿美元的加密资产来清洗所窃取的资金而被判处五年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/leader-of-crypto-heist-worth-billions-gets-five-year-sentence</guid>
